snippet.title: 🆕💥💎 Watercolor Portrait Tips of 🔶Amber Heard 🔶| Watercolor Process 💎💥🆕
snippet.description:
Hello guys!!!
 🆕💥   Amber Heard 💥🆕
🚩🚩🚩step by step  Watercolour  Tutorials   🚩🚩🚩
Secrets of effect with  Watercolour  to get colourful Portrait 
📍📍📍 we used in this video(  Winsor watercolour  )  📍📍📍
In today's video I'll show you easy watercolour painting ideas for beginners step by step that you can use to practice the basic watercolour painting techniques: wet on wet and wet on dry while also practicing different basic washes! I'll show you how to paint eyes effects & wonderful shadows ! Thumbs up for more beautiful scenery & landscape painting ideas! 👍

Use & Enjoy this video
📍For all person who like drawing and real painting 📍
Thanks for visiting our YouTube channel. In this step we share fun easy Ideas, easy way how to with watercolours .Make new visions from arts with best effects.
if you have any suggestions please let us know or if you want any lessons of drawing or painting with any equipment which are your favourite  please let us know .
Thanks so much.
📍 Please be sure to 👁👆 subscribe 👉👁  and share the love with your friends📍
